data.description: Located on a cul-de-sac, and set back on the lot for a larger front yard, this Winding Creek home welcomes you in * Neutral palette throughout main floor * Kitchen offers a large center island, plenty of cabinet and counter space, pantry and recessed lighting *  Kitchen opens to the Family room that has a gas fireplace - Great space for entertaining * Dining space has a vaulted ceiling and direct access to the back deck through the glass sliding door * You will love the Backyard, which backs up to the neighborhood paved path * Half Bath on main floor * Upstairs, the Main Bedroom is fantastic with a large walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom * Each additional bedroom offers a fresh clean space with ample closet space. * Large 2nd Floor Laundry * The Partial finished basement includes a full bathroom with shower and great storage * Additional unfinished basement space (22x18) extends itself to many possibilities * Roof (July 2021) * Water Heater (April 2023) * Community pool, play area, clubhouse & paved paths.  Come see this home today!
